{"tid":1382734,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦一信有感","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:52:39.000Z","uid":93248,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa47a8a6eee44d9f141aacdb8faf1d14aff250d8","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"&quot;政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n可能大家會覺得經過埋721,727事件後<br />\n要醒覺既人一早已經醒覺<br />\n扮訓既人永遠都唔會醒之類...<br />\n<br />\n但現實就係有好多人後知後覺,不知不覺<br />\n今日依然有唔少POST係講自己父母終於由藍轉黃<br />\n証明上一代喺政治上/激進行為既接受能力真係好慢<br />\n但唔代表冇,亦唔代表唔會變<br />\n<br />\n其實由其是所謂和理非,或者唔敢上前線既大家<br />\n係咪應該繼續喺輿論戰度繼續落手呢?<br />\n好似攬炒巴咁,佢繼續用佢地既影響力影響住國際關注<br />\n但我地係咪都應該喺呢方面做返個真真正正既鍵盤戰士呢?<br />\n<br />\n好似上個月咁,大家喺藍營PAGE度玩膠<br />\n其實真係呃到唔少藍絲架喎<br />\n但近呢排大家又好似停晒手,冇晒聲氣咁<br />\n又或者因為覺得冇效而冇再出手?<br />\n原因大概係畀人睇穿手法嘛<br />\n即係話藍絲咁撚蠢都睇得出你地係假藍絲囉<br />\n咁好心大家喺呢方面又發揮下創意,轉下MODE啦<br />\n講創意同適應能力,點講都係我地超晒班啦,<br />\n咁點解唔好好利用呢方面既能力黎做輿論?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11218343cfe70e90864bb7c85a67aa4e057aeec7","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e832ebb9d84b31a0f95af1119388dc1132d2cecc","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840e0ade00a25be62293f204af56ab73167533fd","tid":1382734,"uid":152966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:32:58.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"485f033ab654baecd14c1332d3519036f7a270ee","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得大家禮拜六日就出去<br />\n平日扮工返學咪搞輿論戰囉<br />\n只要有KEYBOARD在手就隨時都可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58aab7a629370d041fe96e80df85ab83340b08ce","tid":1382734,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"咩方法都試"},{"pid":"7b732a55f0f62e5cd671e3ec843ca1e746e00fa6","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58aab7a629370d041fe96e80df85ab83340b08ce","tid":1382734,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"咩方法都試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"同埋趁今日中聯辦開記者會<br />\n順勢咁做會自然好多<br />\n感覺係&ldquo;連中央都出聲你哋都唔支持？想食2家茶禮？&rdquo;<br />\n咁樣班藍絲冇咁易察覺"},{"pid":"9cbefff2d3dd0ee9b6bc27ed512c8addf97b9ee7","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"訓前一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同意又好唔同意都好，起碼交流下集思廣益丫<br />\n而家咁樣彊局法對我地好不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024d3d51e52466c1717da10c7a0aefcf7e9ab9b8","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:52:18.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"33024f8a8e086bdae9ac5ebf8ca3419194112545","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:11:46.000Z","msg":"係咪個TITLE改得柒,唔夠吸睛就冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162dde24c6c7b8b5dd6514c5316a490dd5887779","tid":1382734,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a079db243be19677faa11718364b0280a4317ea","tid":1382734,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"5de03de6c8bc2568d244c9ccb84afcedcad51ba1","tid":1382734,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"開過個TOPIC 啦<br />\nlike<br />\n&quot;場運動就輸了- 天琦要民意,呢排啲兄弟去晒